就扭唔到入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港工程，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好出黎柒啦"},{"pid":"b0293ddecb8e5f06229543fa2af9b6faad647356","tid":951331,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"班 工程撚 扯左得 6mm <br />\n等同無扯到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}